Core Gameplay Pillars:

------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Crossplatform Multiplatform
  - Itchio + Google Firebase Signin + Paypal (In App Purchases) [PC/MOBILE]
  - Itchio + Patreon (Membership Subscription) [PC/MOBILE] 

  - Google Play [Android Phone/Android Tablet/Chromebook]
  - iPhone App Store [iPhone]
  - iPad App Store [iPad]
  - Mac OSx App Store [Macbook Laptop, iMac Desktop, Mac Mini]
  - Microsoft App Store [Windows Laptop, Windows Desktop, Windows Tablet]
  - Steam Wallet [Windows/Mac]

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Performance:
  - 512 or 1024 resolution all models
  - Less than 5 sec load time
  - No slow code functions
  - Above 30fps

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Combat
  - Player Controls
  - Enemy AI
  - Unisex Player
  - Magic Combat Abilities available after beating game from npc

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Hearth
  - Hearth (Home) not only on Earth
  - Customize home with images and music

House Monetization
  - Purchases/Upgrade other settlements to connect them and make them larger
  - Purchase/Upgrade to upload custom in house 3d models and 360 sky 
  - Purchase House Domain Name for links

Settlement Monetization
  - Purchase/Upgrade to get underground Settlements with customizable sims like vroid living in there and the ability to customize them (male/female)
  - Purchase/Upgrade to get synchronus multiplayer

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Interconnected Open Exploration
  - Tropical Desert
  - Portal to Moon

  - Inside Underground Moon
  - Forest in Moon (Underground Forest)

  - Portal to Antartica (Snow Desert Tundra)
  - Underground Antartica (Cave Snow Forest)

  - Portal to Mars
  - Martian Desert
  - Martian Forest
  - Underground Mars Forest

  - Portal Back to Earth Desert Underground
  - Tropical Desert

